---
title: Easy Creamy Double Mustard Chicken & Mash with Steamed Greens
description: Get ready for the ultimate comfort food with a gourmet twist! On the menu tonight we’ve got tender, golden-seared chicken smothered in a luscious, tangy mustard sauce, served over buttery mashed potatoes. On the side, perfectly steamed greens add a fresh, vibrant touch.

